TEXT_ASSET_BTC:
Giới thiệu

Bitcoin là một loại tài sản điện tử và hệ thống thanh toán được phát minh bởi Satoshi Nakamoto - một người/ tổ chức đã công bố các giấy tờ có liên quan vào năm 2008 và phát hành Bitcoin vào năm 2009 dưới dạng phần mềm mã nguồn mở. Với hệ thống xử lý ngang hàng (peer-to-peer), người dùng có thể giao dịch trực tiếp mà không cần thông qua bên trung gian nào.

TEXT_DEPOSIT_DESC:
Otc account and exchange account share one BTC address. When BTC is recharged, information will be shown in your exchange account. Through the transfer function, transferred to OTC account.

Please don’t deposit any other digital assets except BTC to the above address.

Depositing to the above address requires confirmations of the entire network. It will arrive after 10 confirmations.It will take about 10 to 60 mins usually.

Minimum deposit amount:0.02BTC. It won’t be credited less than 0.02BTC.

There is no support for the use of intelligent contracts or block reward (Coinbase) deposit at present.

Your deposit address won’t be changed frequently. Any changes, we will inform you by announcement or email.

Please make sure that your computer and browser are secure and your information is protected from being tampered or leaked.
TEXT_FEE_NOTE:
If there is any changes for transaction fees or effective date, please refer to the official announcement.

Maker fees are paid when you add liquidity to our order book, by placing a limit order under the last trade price for buy and above the last trade price for sell.

Taker fees are paid when you remove liquidity from our order book, by placing any order that is executed against an order of the orderbook. (Please note when your limit order is executed against other user's limit order and his/her order placed earlier than your order, you will pay taker fees.)

Taker means that the limit order or market order you place is executed with the current maker.

When the order you placed is filled by others orders, you need to pay the taker fees.
